thread.title: Jeff

author: Jeff
title: Jeff
text: There were a few times i ordered the BLP-1 resealable LP sleeves, and i was getting with alot of pressing issues (lines across the middle of the sleeve, inconsistant cut on the flap between adhesive and edge 1" area sometimes too long), HOWEVER I believe in this product, and my last two orders have been perfect! Size is correct, no pressing errors!! Good job, thanks, and keep up the good work
